%% Data Flow Diagram - Distributed Workloads
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Test as E2E Test Suite
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KFTO as Training Operator<br/>SA Token
    participant Trainer as Trainer v2 Controller<br/>SA Token
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller<br/>SA Token
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator<br/>SA Token
    participant Master as Master/Head Pod
    participant Workers as Worker Pods
    participant RayDash as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Test,S3: Flow 1: PyTorch Distributed Training (KFTO v1)
        Test->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>KFTO: Watch event
        KFTO->>K8sAPI: Create Master + Worker Pods<br/>SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Master: Schedule Pod
        K8sAPI-->>Workers: Schedule Pods
        Workers->>Master: NCCL communication<br/>dynamic/TCP plaintext
        Workers->>S3: Upload trained model<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS credentials
        Test->>K8sAPI: Poll PyTorchJob status<br/>Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Test,RayDash: Flow 2: Ray Cluster Job Submission
        Test->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>KubeRay: Watch event
        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Head + Worker Pods<br/>SA Token
        Test->>K8sAPI: Create Route/Ingress<br/>Bearer Token
        Test->>RayDash: POST /api/jobs/<br/>HTTP/8265 plaintext No Auth
        RayDash-->>Test: Job ID
        Master->>Workers: Distribute tasks<br/>6379/TCP plaintext
        Test->>RayDash: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP/8265 plaintext
        RayDash-->>Test: Job status + results
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Test,S3: Flow 3: Trainer v2 TrainJob with Kueue
        Test->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterQueue + LocalQueue<br/>Bearer Token
        Test->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Trainer: Watch event
        Trainer->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Kueue: Watch Workload
        Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload<br/>SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Workers: Schedule Training Pods
        Workers->>S3: Download datasets<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS credentials
        Workers->>S3: Upload model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS credentials
        Test->>K8sAPI: Poll TrainJob status<br/>Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Test,Prom: Metrics Validation
        Test->>Prom: Query training metrics<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>Test: Metric values
    end
